item.title: Reflecting Myself: 2020
item.description: this blogpost is part of the assigment given to us on course ENGT 102. Just posting because it reminds me of my shortcomings. Handling the situation: The train is out of the track; Deviated from its journey. Looks like its heading the opposite path. How can i bring it back? I should assess the situation, understand the condition, and make plans according to it but Somehow my brain manages to abstract things out.
